Drop the licensed webfont files into this folder. Required filenames (must match exactly):

  MartinaPlantijn-Regular.woff2   — Martina Plantijn, weight 400
  MartinaPlantijn-Medium.woff2    — Martina Plantijn, weight 500
  Geograph-Regular.woff2          — Geograph, weight 400

These filenames are referenced directly in the @font-face rules in index.html.
Until the files are present, the site falls back gracefully to Georgia (serif) and
system sans-serif fonts and still looks fine.
